{"type":"message","id":"47fb2a68","parentId":"bc26fbf6","timestamp":"2026-03-18T01:27:36.886Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Y6qh1gQlwCGRbcq7IM0xlGqE","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-channel-rules\ndescription: |\n  Lark/Feishu channel output rules. Always active in Lark conversations.\nalwaysActive: true\n---\n\n# Lark Output Rules\n\n## Writing Style\n\n- Short, conversational, low ceremony — talk like a coworker, not a manual\n- Prefer plain sentences over bullet lists when a brief answer suffices\n- Get to the point and stop — no need for a summary paragraph every time\n\n## Note\n\n- Lark Markdown differs from standard Markdown in some ways; when unsure, refer to `references/markdown-syntax.md`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773797256883}}
{"type":"message","id":"9bdadc30","parentId":"47fb2a68","timestamp":"2026-03-18T01:27:45.046Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 早，老大。我是麻辣龙虾 🦞，还在，还是那个冷静但不端着的版本。今天想让我处理点什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1274,"output":46,"cacheRead":35072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36392,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773797256887}}
{"type":"message","id":"15800605","parentId":"9bdadc30","timestamp":"2026-03-18T01:27:46.088Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54abb9e908b4b10635db382901e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 09:27 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54abb9e908b4b10635db382901e]\nou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3: {\n admin off\n auto_https disable_redirects\n default_sni 127.0.0.1\n skip_install_trust\n storage file_system {\n root /data/caddy\n }\n}\n\nhttps://127.0.0.1:8443 {\n bind 0.0.0.0\n tls internal\n reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:18789\n} 解毒这个配置"}],"timestamp":1773797266086}}
{"type":"message","id":"c519005d","parentId":"15800605","timestamp":"2026-03-18T01:28:21.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Explaining Caddy config**\n\nI need to explain the Caddy config related to \"解毒,\" which likely means to sanitize or clarify it. There's a need to address any dangerous elements. I should consider that the user hasn’t asked for prior context and might be referring to a typo with \"解毒\" rather than \"解读.\" It seems they want to understand what the config does and its implications, so I'll suggest a safer version. Let's get concise with this!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 这是个很简陋的 Caddy 配置，作用其实就两件事：**本地签发证书**，然后把 **8443 端口的 HTTPS 请求反代到 127.0.0.1:18789**。\n\n逐段看：\n\n`admin off`\n- 关掉 Caddy 的管理 API。\n- 好处是少一个暴露面，配置不能通过 API 动态改。\n\n`auto_https disable_redirects`\n- 关闭“自动把 HTTP 跳到 HTTPS”的行为。\n- 不等于关闭 HTTPS，只是别指望它自动做 80→443 跳转。\n\n`default_sni 127.0.0.1`\n- 给没有 SNI 的 TLS 请求一个默认主机名。\n- 这里设成 `127.0.0.1` 比较怪，但因为你下面就是本地自签证书场景，算是硬糊上去能跑。\n\n`skip_install_trust`\n- 用 `tls internal` 时，Caddy 不会把自己的根证书自动装进系统信任链。\n- 所以浏览器/客户端大概率会报“证书不受信任”，除非你手动信任那套内部 CA。\n\n`storage file_system { root /data/caddy }`\n- Caddy 的证书、状态之类持久化到 `/data/caddy`。\n\n下面这个站点块：\n\n`https://127.0.0.1:8443 {`\n- 监听 `8443`，站点名是 `127.0.0.1`。\n\n`bind 0.0.0.0`\n- 重点：**不是只监听本机**，而是对所有网卡开放。\n- 也就是说，只要防火墙没拦，别人可以从网络上访问你这台机器的 8443。\n\n`tls internal`\n- 用 Caddy 自己内部 CA 签发证书。\n- 适合内网、自用、测试，不适合公网正式环境。\n\n`reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:18789`\n- 所有进来的 HTTPS 请求都转发到本机 `18789` 端口。\n\n所以整体翻成人话就是：\n\n> “在所有网卡上开放一个 8443 的 HTTPS 入口，用内部自签证书给 `127.0.0.1` 提供 TLS，然后把请求转给本机 18789 服务。”\n\n几个明显问题：\n\n1. **`bind 0.0.0.0` + `https://127.0.0.1:8443` 组合有点拧巴**\n   - 证书是给 `127.0.0.1` 的。\n   - 但服务却对外网卡开放。\n   - 外部用户如果不是用 `https://127.0.0.1:8443` 访问，证书名基本对不上。\n\n2. **`tls internal` 只适合内网/本机**\n   - 外部设备访问会有证书信任问题。\n   - 如果这是想对公网提供服务，这配置不合适。\n\n3. **没有 HTTP 入口**\n   - 也没有自动跳转。\n   - 就是纯 8443 HTTPS 入口。\n\n如果你的目标是：\n\n### 1）只想本机安全访问\n那更合理写成：\n\n```caddy\n{\n\tadmin off\n\tskip_install_trust\n\tstorage file_system {\n\t\troot /data/caddy\n\t}\n}\n\nhttps://127.0.0.1:8443 {\n\tbind 127.0.0.1\n\ttls internal\n\treverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:18789\n}\n```\n\n这样才是真的“只本机可用”。\n\n### 2）想让局域网别的机器访问\n那应该用实际 IP 或域名，比如：\n\n```caddy\nhttps://192.168.1.10:8443 {\n\ttls internal\n\treverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:18789\n}\n```\n\n或者更好，用内网域名。\n\n### 3）想正式对外提供服务\n那就该换成真实域名，让 Caddy 自动申请公开证书，不要 `tls internal`：\n\n```caddy\nexample.com {\n\treverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:18789\n}\n```\n\n如果你愿意，我可以顺手帮你把这份配置按你的真实目标改成一版能直接用的。你告诉我它是要：\n- 仅本机访问\n- 局域网访问\n- 公网访问  \n我直接给你成品。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":464,"output":1197,"cacheRead":36224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37885,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773797266087}}
